insights: Donald Trump's April 2025 physical exam at Walter Reed National Military Medical Center reported him in "excellent cognitive and physical health."
He achieved a perfect score (30/30) on the Montreal Cognitive Assessment (MoCA).
As of April 2025, his height was 6'3" (75 inches) and weight was 224 pounds, giving him a BMI of 28.1 (no longer considered obese, down from 243-244 pounds previously).
